      "source": [
        "This code cell calculates and prints the following descriptive statistics for the `data` array:\n",
        "- **Mean**: The average value of the dataset.\n",
        "- **Median**: The middle value of the dataset when sorted.\n",
        "- **Variance**: A measure of how spread out the data is from the mean (average of the squared differences from the mean).\n",
        "- **Standard Deviation**: The square root of the variance, providing a measure of the typical distance between data points and the mean."
